Package: RFM_Segmentation
Type: Project
Title: A Shiny App with RFM Analysis
Version: 0.1.0-beta
Author: Mladen <mladenmijatovic216@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Mladen <mladenmijatovic216@gmail.com>
Description: RFM application is a Shiny app that allows users to perform RFM (Recency, Frequency, Monetary) analysis for customers and locations.
